											<section class="main bio authorbio">
							<h3 class="invis">Author bio</h3>
																																															<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/moira-donovan/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_bottom" >
											<div class="container col3 ">
												<div class="col span2"><p>Moira Donovan is an independent journalist and radio producer based on the East Coast of Canada, with a body of work focused on the environment and climate change. Her work has appeared in the <em>Christian Science Monitor</em>, <em>Vice</em>, and <em>The Walrus</em>, and has aired on CBC Radio.</p></div>
												<div class="singlebioimage col nomobile"><img width="400" height="400" src="https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/moira-donovan.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-post-image" alt="Moira Donovan" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/moira-donovan.jpg 400w, https://hakaimagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/moira-donovan-150x150.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" /></div>
											</div>
											</a>
																															</section>
										<hr class="fullwidth" />
										<section class="metadata main">
